        <h2>Our 2040 Net-Zero Commitment</h2>
        <p>In 2024, Acme Chemicals announced science-based net-zero targets aligned with the Paris Agreement's 1.5°C pathway. Our commitment covers Scope 1, 2, and 3 emissions across our entire value chain.</p>
        <p>Backed by a $400M investment over 10 years, our decarbonization program focuses on process electrification, renewable energy, bio-based feedstock transition, and supplier engagement.</p>
        <ul class="check-list">
          <li>50% absolute Scope 1 & 2 reduction by 2030 (vs. 2019)</li>
          <li>30% Scope 3 intensity reduction by 2030</li>
          <li>100% renewable electricity across all plants by 2032</li>
          <li>Net-zero across all emissions by 2040</li>
        </ul>
        <br>
        <a href="/contact/" class="btn btn-primary">Download ESG Report 2024</a>
