        <h2>Green Chemistry by Design</h2>
        <p>We apply the 12 Principles of Green Chemistry to every new product development program. This means designing for reduced hazard, minimal waste, energy efficiency, and safer solvents from the start — not as an afterthought.</p>
        <p>Our Green Chemistry Index rates all new product candidates against biodegradability, bioaccumulation potential, aquatic toxicity, and renewable content benchmarks before approval for development.</p>
